<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-12 17:25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Gore says Bradley's no 'real Democrat,' Bradley offers return to  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
    	   SAN JOSE, Calif. (AP) - With the room stacked against him and polls
