<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-12 18:47 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> More Jets Found With Tail Problems  </HEADLINE>
   By LEON DROUIN KEITH Associated Press Writer
<TEXT>
<P>
